Package agend932

Class Media

java.lang.Object
agend932.Media
public class Media
extends Object
Represents a media item scraped from Metacritic, encapsulating all the relevant details of a media entity such as a game, movie, or TV show.

    • Media

      public Media​(String mediaType, String pictureUrl, String title, String description, String platform, String genre, String releaseDate, String ratedScore, String originalURL, String metascore, String extraInfo)
      Constructs a new Media object with detailed information.
      Parameters:
      mediaType - The type of the media (e.g., game, movie, tv).
      pictureUrl - The URL of the media's thumbnail image.
      title - The title of the media.
      description - A brief description of the media.
      platform - The platform for which the media is available.
      genre - The genre of the media.
      releaseDate - The release date of the media.
      ratedScore - The score rated by users.
      originalURL - The original URL to the media's Metacritic page.
      metascore - The metascore assigned by Metacritic.
      extraInfo - Any additional information available for the media.
